    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for checking out my car! Honestly, it\u2019s been such a fantastic ride and has served me so well. It\u2019s in really solid condition and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants something dependable and ready to hit the road today. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
