    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a well-cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and value. The exterior retains its classic luster, showing only the light, honest character marks one would expect from careful daily use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a remarkably clean cabin; the seating surfaces are supple and free of significant wear, while the dashboard and controls remain crisp and fully functional. Mechanically, this car is in its prime, delivering a smooth, responsive drive thanks to a consistent maintenance schedule. From the cold-blowing A/C to the steady idle, every system has been vetted for reliability. This is an ideal choice for a driver seeking a dependable, attractive vehicle that has many miles of adventure left to offer.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
