    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it for its next owner. It runs great, looks sharp, and has been super dependable for me. If you\u2019re looking for a smooth ride that\u2019s been well-cared for, this is the one! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
