      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering a 7,900 RPM redline and 333 horsepower through individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and the M-Variable Lock differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Koni adjustable dampers, providing exceptional turn-in and mid-corner stability. While the finish shows minor road-going patina consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains tight with linear power delivery and a visceral exhaust note. A turn-key enthusiast vehicle optimized for performance.",
